<div class="mb-6"><a href="/admin/membership" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 no-underline">← 멤버십 대시보드</a></div>

<% if (!policy) { %>
<div class="mb-4 p-4 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg text-amber-800">활성 평가 정책이 없습니다.</div>
<% } else if (policy.downgrade_mode === 'NONE') { %>
<div class="mb-4 p-4 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg text-blue-800">현재 정책은 <b>강등하지 않음</b>으로 설정돼 있어 강등 예정자가 없습니다.</div>
<% } %>

<div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-between">
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">유지 기준 미달로 다음 정기 평가 시 강등될 회원입니다. (등급 고정 회원 제외)</p>
  <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-red-50 text-red-700 text-sm font-medium"><%= candidates.length %>명</span>
</div>

<div class="bg-white overflow-hidden shadow-sm rounded-lg overflow-x-auto">
  <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
    <thead class="bg-gray-50"><tr>
      <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">회원</th>
      <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">현재 → 예상</th>
      <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">인정금액</th>
      <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">주문건수</th>
    </tr></thead>
    <tbody class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200">
      <% if (!candidates || candidates.length === 0) { %>
      <tr><td colspan="4" class="px-6 py-8 text-center text-gray-500">강등 예정자가 없습니다.</td></tr>
      <% } else { candidates.forEach(function(c){ %>
      <tr>
        <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm"><%= c.userName || '-' %><br><span class="text-xs text-gray-400"><%= c.email %></span></td>
        <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-center"><span class="text-gray-500"><%= c.fromGradeName || '-' %></span> → <span class="font-medium text-red-600"><%= c.toGradeName || '-' %></span></td>
        <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-right"><%= Number(c.amount).toLocaleString() %>원</td>
        <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-right"><%= Number(c.count) %></td>
      </tr>
      <% }); } %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400">사전 안내는 <code>scripts/membership_demotion_notice_cron.sh</code>(월 배치)가 이메일로 통지합니다. 강등은 정기 평가(<code>calc_membership_grade.js</code>)에서 실제 반영됩니다.</p>
